# Expo SDK 56

Docs: https://docs.expo.dev/versions/v56.0.0/

## Stack

- expo ~56, react-native 0.85, react 19.2
- react-native-reanimated 4.3.1 + react-native-worklets 0.8.3 (required pair)
- react-native-gesture-handler ~2.31.1
- @react-native-async-storage/async-storage 2.2.0

## Dev

- Handheld testing: `npm run start:tunnel` or `npx expo start -c --tunnel`
- `EXPO_UNSTABLE_HEADLESS=1` set in default start script
- Do not bump SDK or Reanimated without user approval and doc review

## Env

Firebase keys use `EXPO_PUBLIC_*` in `.env` (see `.env.example`). Guest mode works without Firebase.
